---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import DarkHeader from '../../components/DarkHeader.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Mustang Mach E Material Flows — Cooper Minehart"
  description="Interactive Sankey and geographic flow map of the Mustang Mach-E battery supply chain — Extended Range NMC and Standard Range LFP, from mine to pack."
>
  <DarkHeader>
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 pt-12 pb-10">
      <p class="section-label-light mb-3">Research · Mach-E Material Flows</p>
      <h1 class="font-serif text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-3">
        Mustang Mach E Material Flows
      </h1>
      <p class="text-stone-300 max-w-2xl leading-relaxed">
        Two Mach-E trims, same Cuautitl&aacute;n line, very different chains.
        Interactive flows from mining to pack.
      </p>
    </div>
  </DarkHeader>

  <article class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 pt-10 pb-24 text-[#1a1a1a]">

    <div class="prose-content space-y-5 text-[15px] leading-relaxed">
      <p>
        The Mach-E is a natural experiment that demonstrates how a company
        designs supply chains with and without domestic and FEOC constraints.
        Both Mach-E trims came off the same Cuautitl&aacute;n line, with very
        different battery supply chains: NMC in the Extended Range, LFP in the
        Standard Range. I built a material-flow diagram from the mine to the
        pack.
      </p>
      <p>
        <a
          href="https://cooperminehart.substack.com/"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener"
          class="text-forest-600 hover:underline font-medium"
        >
          Read the full essay on Substack &rarr;
        </a>
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Interactive 1: Mach-E Sankey -->
    <figure class="mt-12 mb-4">
      <div class="border border-stone-200 rounded-lg overflow-hidden bg-white shadow-sm">
        <iframe
          src="/maps/mache-sankey.html"
          title="Mustang Mach-E supply chain Sankey, Extended Range NMC and Standard Range LFP"
          class="w-full block"
          style="height: 90vh; min-height: 760px; border: 0;"
          loading="lazy"
        />
      </div>
      <figcaption class="text-xs text-[#888] mt-3 text-center">
        Mach-E supply-chain Sankey: Extended Range (NMC, 91 kWh) and Standard
        Range (LFP, 70 kWh), per-pack mass in kg.
      </figcaption>
    </figure>

    <!-- Interactive 2: NMC geographic flow map -->
    <figure class="mt-12 mb-4">
      <div class="border border-stone-200 rounded-lg overflow-hidden bg-white shadow-sm">
        <iframe
          src="/maps/nmc-flow.html"
          title="Mach-E Extended Range NMC supply chain — geographic flow map"
          class="w-full block"
          style="height: 75vh; min-height: 600px; border: 0;"
          loading="lazy"
        />
      </div>
      <figcaption class="text-xs text-[#888] mt-3 text-center">
        NMC supply chain by weight per pack &mdash; arcs colored by material,
        widths scaled by mass. Toggle materials with the layer control on the
        upper right.
      </figcaption>
    </figure>

    <!-- footer -->
    <div class="mt-16 pt-8 border-t border-stone-200">
      <p class="text-xs font-mono text-[#888] uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">
        Sources &amp; data
      </p>
      <p class="text-sm text-[#555] leading-relaxed mb-4">
        Ford FY2024 10-K &middot; Ford 2023 Integrated Sustainability Report
        &middot; Hunan Yuneng Shenzhen Stock Exchange prospectus &middot;
        Yunnan Yuntianhua annual report &middot; GREET 2023 &middot; BatPaC v5
        &middot; USGS Mineral Commodity Summaries 2024 &middot; IEA Critical
        Minerals Market Review 2023 &middot; OBBBA H.R. 1 (P.L. 119-21).
      </p>
      <p class="text-sm">
        <a
          href="https://github.com/cminehar-coder/critical-minerals-research"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener"
          class="text-forest-600 hover:underline font-medium"
        >
          Source data &amp; build scripts &rarr;
        </a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </article>
</Layout>
